<SYNC Start=967551><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=967717><P Class=KRCC>
그런 면에서...
<SYNC Start=969469><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=969552><P Class=KRCC>
어...
<SYNC Start=970724><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=972555><P Class=KRCC>
